This is a Sample Certification Authority using openssl. This Authority 
consists in some sample scripts and is usefull for others as well,
oder so


Um einen neuen request zu generieren benutzt du:

openssl req -newkey rsa:4096 -keyout key.pem -out req.pem
Wichtisch Organisation Name muss "president.eu.org" sein!!!!!


#################################################################
# enterprise key erzeugung 
#################################################################
cdirect@zvadm1:/opt/cdirect/CA > openssl pkcs8 -topk8 -in certs/enterprise.pem  -in private/enterprise.pem  -out enterprise.pkcs 
Enter Encryption Password:
Verifying - Enter Encryption Password:
cdirect@zvadm1:/opt/cdirect/CA > cat enterprise.pkcs 




'''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''''

cdirect@zvadm1:/opt/cdirect/CA > openssl pkcs12 -export -in certs/client.pem  -inkey private/client.pem  
